entries.name: Metis Multisig
entries.description: Can pause, censor, instantly upgrade the bridge and upgrade other critical contracts in the system.

entries.name: Lib_AddressManager
entries.description: Legacy contract used to manage a mapping of string names to addresses. Modern OP stack uses a different standard proxy system instead, but this contract is still necessary for backwards compatibility with several older contracts.

StateCommitmentChain.description: Manages the L2 state on Ethereum. L2 state batches can be appended here by proposers.
